name: Leven Rose Jojoba Oil Organic, Pure Cold Pressed Natural Unrefined Moisturizer for Skin Hair and Nails 4 oz
ingredients: 100% Pure unrefined and organic Jojoba Oil from Simmondsia chinensis grown in Arizona, cold pressed. Leven Rose Jojoba Oil is Cold Pressed by using an expeller, which is a screw like mechanism that presses out the oil (actually a wax) without heating up the oil. Keeping the oil from getting too hot is extremely important. If the Jojoba oil gets hot, certain properties of the oil are lost, leaving it much less effective, and beneficial. Leven Rose Jojoba Oil is also unrefined, leaving the essential nutrients and fatty acids in the oil.
